creator: App-vise
descriptionHtml:
Discover local student-run events and associations at your university. Manage your profile to find events that directly match your interests or expand your search to explore new opportunities! Swipe through events effortlessly to add them to your favourites. Need more information or want to set a reminder? Simply tap on the event! You can search for upcoming events on the in-app calendar, go to the tickets page immediately or see what’s happening in other cities.

Uni-Life helps make the hectic student life more structured and ensures you won’t miss out on anything!

As a student:
• Interact with events by swiping right to add them to your in-app calendar if you’re interested or left to never see them again
• Click on events to see the description, time, date and location
• Go straight to the tickets or sign up page
• Manage your profile by identifying key interests and opportunities, including associations activities, sports, fields of interest, work opportunities and more
• Use the in-app calendar to look at all events or add filters to see what’s happening today, tomorrow, next week and next month
• Personalised overview in your calendar based on events you liked

As an association:
• Locate all potentially interested students
• Sustainable way to promote on and off campus
• Instantly upload any event without waiting times
• Clear overview of all your posted events
• See how popular your events are on the dashboard (coming soon!)

Download now and start your Uni-Life!

*Current Partners*
Uni-Life works with partner universities. This means we first get in contact with universities and set them up as a partner before they become visible on the app. The list below shows which universities we currently work with. If your university is not on the list yet, you can sign them up through our website: www.uni-life.nl.

• Erasmus University Rotterdam
• Amsterdam University College
• Leiden University College The Hague
• University College Groningen
• University College Maastricht
• University College Roosevelt
• University College Tilburg
• University College Twente
• University College Utrecht
descriptionShort: Uni-Life is the place for students to find all university events!
title: Uni-Life

creator: Uni-Life
descriptionHtml:
Uni-Life is the best way to discover the full student life at your university. Whether you’re looking to make new friends, find the best parties or join an association, we’ve got you covered🚀

What can you do?
- Chat with other students in one of the many communities
- Meet other students directly through the meet-ups
- Find all events hosted by student clubs & associations
- Get the latest news and announcements on campus
- Find your own buddy (or offer to be one yourself!)
- Get an overview of all campus organizations
- Get notified whenever something relevant is happening
- And much more!

Download the app now and start your Uni-Life!

Current Partners:

Uni-Life works with partner universities. This means we first get in contact with universities and set them up as a partner before they become visible on the app. If your university is not on the list yet, you can request them through our website: www.uni-life.nl

creator: Uni-Life
descriptionHtml:
Our biggest app update yet, so you can make the most of your student life!

Discover everything your university has to offer with Uni-Life. Whether you’re looking to make new friends, find the best student events, or find out about the associations, we’ve got you covered:

Stay in the loop: Read posts by other students at your university and reply to them. Someone looking for a fourth person for a padel match? You’re in!
Post something yourself: Start a conversation in less than a minute. Looking for a second-hand bike? Maybe just general advice to find housing?
Find like-minded students: Browse through the students at your university and filter by interests, country of origin and studies. Found a match? Send them a private message!

Coming soon: Events calendar, associations overview, student group chats and much more. Make sure you have the automatic app updates on.

Download the app now and start your Uni-Life!


Current Partners:
Uni-Life works with partner universities. This means we first get in contact with universities and set them up as a partner before they become visible on the app. If your university is not on the list yet, you can request them through our website: www.uni-life.nl

What’s new?
New features to make the most of your Uni-life!
Student Posts: Create and reply to posts from fellow students.
Connect with Like-Minded Students: Filter by start year, country, interests, and study. Find them on the list and start a chat!
